WEBVTT

00:10:28.784 --> 00:10:32.091
his colleagues would say
things to him like,

00:10:32.115 --> 00:10:33.899
"Hey, did you fry him?"

00:10:33.923 --> 00:10:35.694
To them, it was just a joke.

00:10:36.885 --> 00:10:38.677
Then there was Jon.

00:10:38.701 --> 00:10:43.080
Jon said his decision weighed on him,

00:10:43.104 --> 00:10:45.050
and it burdened him daily.

00:10:46.558 --> 00:10:49.619
The final juror that I spoke to was Ken.

00:10:49.643 --> 00:10:51.916
Ken was the foreman of the jury.

00:10:53.078 --> 00:10:54.747
When we sat down to talk,

00:10:56.485 --> 00:11:02.751
it was apparent that he was deeply
saddened by what we were required to do.